{"tid":1980219,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗稱中聯辦亦要遵守本港法律　並非不受管束","createTime":"2020-04-20T02:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T04:18:14.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"973b0adb0c22fc8c0c856a2206a5f8ca72f2cb44","tid":1980219,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委譚耀宗認為，中央政府有責任監督《基本法》的執行情況，而港澳辦及中聯辦正是中央政府負責港澳事務的代表。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗又指，雖然《基本法》沒有列明相關情況，但兩辦既然代表中央政府， 本港出現違反《基本法》的情況，例如有人阻止立法會的立法工作，就要發聲，認為兩辦因為本港有人違反《基本法》而發聲，並非干預，並藉今次事件清楚交代職責。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗表示，兩辦獲中央政府授權，直接代表中央政府處理港澳事務，所以並非「中央人民政府所屬各部門」，而特區政府以往的說法，可能反映政府對內地架構未必準確掌握，指中聯辦既要執行中央政府指示，代表中央政府執行《基本法》，亦要遵守本港法律，並非不受管束。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521571-20200420.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521571-20200420.htm&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPuTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=142f57ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521571-20200420.htm&h=e27158eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521571-20200420.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/a3/KkbnN.gif/revision/latest/top-crop/width/150/height/150?cb=20110710090638\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fa%2Fa3%2FKkbnN.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Ftop-crop%2Fwidth%2F150%2Fheight%2F150%3Fcb%3D20110710090638&h=ffb63d98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9091b09c2694f7c46ed2b922f10350785d7a1bc7","tid":1980219,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"一時又話要一時話唔使,想模糊焦點？<br />\n咁守唔守廿二條呀"},{"pid":"047162a4c777fdab48031e2c0fc26a9bab8be14d","tid":1980219,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T03:05:45.000Z","msg":"風向無時無刻都變緊，一起身睇新聞個個 d 口風都唔同晒"},{"pid":"c40000b